        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-white">Revisions and Errata</h2>
        <p class="pb-5 dark:text-white">
          The materials appearing on Blue Skies Above Website may include
          technical, typographical, or photographic errors. Blue Skies Above
